@startuml create-user-structure
title Create User Process

start

:Open "Create User" form;

:Enter user details;
note right
  - **Username:** Unique identifier for the user.
  - **Password:** Secure password for account access.
  - **Confirm Password:** Re-enter password for verification.
  - **Role:** Defines user permissions (e.g., Admin, Editor, Viewer).
  - **Email:** User's contact email address.
  - **Document Role:** Specifies access level to documents.
end note

:Click "Create User" button;

:System validates entered details;

if (Validation Successful?) then (yes)
    :Create user account successfully;
    :Display confirmation message;
else (no)
    :Display error message indicating the issue;
    :Prompt to correct errors;
endif

stop
@enduml
